"Lieferung."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Manufacturing App</b>:</font> Level up "
"your production processes, managing Bills of Materials (BoMs) and work "
"centers efficiently."
msgstr ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Fertigungsapp-</b>:</font> Optimieren Sie "
"Ihre Produktionsprozesse und verwalten Sie Stücklisten und Arbeitsplätze "
"effizient."

#. module: textile_manufacturing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:textile_manufacturing.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Project App</b>:</font> Collaborate on pre-"
